items.description:
"Recognizable by their thick beards and faces carved from flesh, the Eastern Garks have a brutal temperament but are skilled strategists, able to work effectively in teams. They are often clad in animal skins, long dark cloaks bearing the emblem of their clan, and are renowned for their expertise in forging thick armor.

In order to draw in the warmth of the sun, they bear black tattoos on their bodies and faces, further accentuating their intimidating appearance. Also known as the Estarsitz, they generally worship Nihilum or more commonly, Iracundus."

I recommend using the trigger words "GarkEst" and "warrior," but you can replace "warrior" with other professions.

I hope you enjoy using this model. Please feel free to provide feedback on its strengths and weaknesses.

items.name: Tone Range Compressor (VAE)
items.description:
You generally like the checkpoint that is freely available, but its author set the noise offset value too high. Familiar situation? This VAE is designed to solve this problem. In the language of photography, it compresses the tone range histogram of generation from both sides closer to the center, the exposure hardly changes. In simple terms, it only changes the contrast, without affecting the brightness of the midtones. In fact, this is a regular vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned, but with a number of mathematical transformations on its input and output layers.

您一般喜欢免费提供的检查点，但其作者将噪声偏移值设置得太高。熟悉的情况吗？这个 VAE 旨在解决这个问题。用摄影的语言来说，它将生成的色调范围直方图从两侧压缩到中心附近，曝光几乎不变。简单地说，它只改变对比度，不影响中间色调的亮度。事实上，这是一个普通的 vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned，但在其输入和输出层上有一些数学变换。

Вам, в целом, нравится выложенный в свободный доступ чекпоинт, но его автор выставил слишком большое значение смещения шума. Знакомая ситуация? Данный VAE призван решить эту проблему. Выражаясь языком фотографии, сжимая гистограмму тонального диапазона генерации с двух сторон ближе к центру, экспозиция почти не меняется. Проще говоря, меняем только контраст, не затрагивая яркость полутонов. Фактически, это обычный vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned, но с рядом математических преобразований на его входных и выходных слоях.

items.name: Freedom.Redmond
items.description:
Freedom.Redmond is here!

You can currently test it at this link thanks to the makeai. run API.

I'm grateful for the GPU time from Redmond.AI that allowed me to finish this model!

This is a generalist model fine-tuned on SD 2.1 768X with a focus on generating images in >1024x.

The model has a high capacity to generate realistic, artistic images, cars, people, and a wide variety of themes. It's a versatile model.

This model will serve as the basis for a dozen models and LORAs that will come specialized in specific themes.

I highly recommend DPM+ SDE/2M or 2M SDE settings with 30 Steps. In resolution above 768x.

I also recommend testing some prompts with or without negative prompts as there are cases where the results are also interesting without negatives.

I really hope you like the model and use it.

If you like the model and think it's worth it, you can make a donation to my Patreon or Ko-fi.

I want to give a huge thanks to the people who helped me these past three months:

Mousewrites, PeePa, Kaz, Queria Star Morta, theovercomer8, Nawnie, Freon, Kohya

Follow me in my twitter to know before all about new models:

https://twitter.com/artificialguybr/

Update: I have authorized commercial use of the model in image generation services. You just have to explicitly credit me @artificialguybr (thanks if you link to my twitter account).

items.name: Master Tigress [Kung Fu Panda]
items.description:
A LoRA for our lovely Master Tigress!

V1

The Lora is trained on 30 selected images of Tigress. Training includes NSFW and SFW work, so both output types are possible.

2 Epochs at 1500 Samples each at 768x768 with bucketing.

Suggested use:

I suggest the weights stay between 0.5 and 0.8 for best results (see example images).

The trigger word is "master_tigress".

Other helpful prompts include:

  • detailed red eyes

  • yellow sclera

V2

Trained on more images and with a larger resolution.

Suggested use:

I suggest the weights stay between 0.3 and 0.7 for best results (see example images).

The trigger word is "master_tigress".

Other helpful prompts include:

  • detailed red eyes

  • yellow sclera

To get here usual outfit, you may use

  • chinese clothing, vest

Known Issues:

The model really wants to output NSFW images, except if prompted negatively against it.
When you get non-perfect eyes, copy the image to inpaint and let it run on just the eyes again.

items.name: Black Cauldron - Princess Eilonwy
items.description:
If you like the LoRa, please feel free to share your generated images here and leave a review (or at least a rating) for the sake of motivation and stuff ;D

For usage guidance, look into the About this version box for more information and click on Show more to get all trigger words and combinations (The trigger words in the Details box are a pain to manage).

Please contact me here on civitAi or on Twitter if you want to provide the LoRa in a generation service.

About

This character has been suggested by a user here on civitai (one of the rare cases where I will follow such a suggestion, my stance on suggestions for characters is still as follows: I don't do it unless it's a character I like, because wasting time and energy on a character I simply don't care about (quite literally in the case of training ;D) is something I don't like.

Anyway, back to the character and the film, The Black Cauldron is a really good Disneyfilm with a princess who doesn't sing and is not delusional like the other princesses (hmmm maybe thats one of the key attributes that makes a disney princess a disney princess?) All that makes the whole movie 5x better (I really don't like the singing part in any Disneyfilm).

Its a shame that its pretty much a forgotten disney movie (Its not really featured on disney+ and Eilonwy doesnt really count as a Disney princess which is weird because even Merida aka the girl from the other studio counts as disney princess. But maybe its because Eilonwy is not the protagonist of the story?) Well whatever, If you haven't seen the movie yet, watch it, it is a nice change from the usual Disney stuff.

Training

I collected 82 images from Eilonwy for training...

Beside Eilonwy I collected images for Taran and Fflewddur Fflam but I will do the training for them some time in the future.

items.name: foot up/foot/foot focus/barefoot
items.description:
这不能算是一个正式的版本，因为它不够稳定，达不到我的预期。

在过去的几天里我都在制作这个Lora，废弃了很多个版本，总是不能得到令我满意的结果，它实在是很难控制，跟AI稳定生成手一样困难。这个发布的版本只能说勉强可以使用，它不可避免得会出现错误的脚掌，以及多指或者少指的情况，我建议在权重0.6~0.8使用它，需要触发词foot up，需要主体词1girl或者其他角色Lora，否则可能只会生成脚。

最好是不要加姿势tag，可能会出现更加严重的肢体变形。

我建议可以多生成几张，把没有问题的放大，放大的重绘幅度最好是0.3。

建议只生成裸足，因为我还没有在学习库中加入丝袜。

我会继续优化这个Lora，直到它的错误率下降，请关注后续更新~

This is not an official release because it is not stable enough to meet my expectations.

In the past few days I have been working on this Lora, discarded many versions, always can not get satisfactory results, it is really difficult to control, just like the AI stable generation of hands. This released version can only be said to be barely usable, it will inevitably have wrong feet and the situation of too many or too few toes.

I suggest using it in the weight 0.6~0.8, which requires the trigger word foot up, the main word 1girl or other characters Lora, otherwise it may only generate feet.

It is best not to add a pose tag, which may cause more serious limb deformation.

I suggest that can generate more photos and enlarge the ones that have no problems, and the redrawing amplitude of amplification is preferably 0.3.

I recommend only generating bare feet because I haven't added stockings to my library yet.

I will continue to optimize this Lora until its error rate drops, please stay tuned for future updates ~

items.name: Peugeot 306 Maxi
items.description:
After 95 models, 384 hours of processing, 2000 likes and 15K downloads, I want to sincerely thank the 5 people in total who supported me and allowed me to credit my colab. You made all this possible.

The Peugeot 306 is a small family car built by the French car manufacturer Peugeot from 1993 to 2002. It replaced the 309. Peugeot gave the 306 many updates and aesthetic changes to keep up with the competition, and it was replaced by the 307 in 2001. Cabriolet and estate versions continued until 2002. Versions were built in Argentina by Sevel from 1996 to 2002.

The Peugeot 306 Maxi competed in Group A of the French and World Rally Championship. The GTI version of the car also won the Spa 24 hours endurance race in 1999 and 2000.

The car took the Danish Touringcar Championship in 1999, 2000 and 2001, and the Asian Touring Car Series title in 2000, 2001 and 2002.
